    <abstract>
      <t>   This document defines PRE-RCT, the Pre-Execution Authorization
   Receipt, a cryptographically signed and attestation-aware receipt
   format used to record high-risk authorization events.  PRE-RCT is
   intended for use with pre-execution authorization protocols such as
   GNA.

	 </t>
